  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  males and females,

          -  between 18 and 75 year old

          -  who present a burned surface more than 30% of the body surface

          -  who need catecholamine infusion

          -  between J0 and J3 after the injury.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  pregnancy,

          -  trauma,

          -  sepsis,

          -  cardiac insufficiency,

          -  AIDS,

          -  etomidate administration
      </textblock>
